text: Prey Phkoam Commune () is a khum (commune) in Angkor Borei District, Takéo Province, Cambodia. == Administration == As of 2019, the commune has 6 phums (villages) as follows. {| class="wikitable sortable" !No. !Code !Village !Khmer |- !1 |21010601 |Prey Phkoam Ka |ព្រៃផ្គាំ ក |- !2 |21010602 |Prey Phkoam Kha |ព្រៃផ្គាំ ខ |- !3 |21010603 |Prey Phkoam Ko |ព្រៃផ្គាំ គ |- !4 |21010604 |Trong Phum |ទ្រង់់ភូមិ |- !5 |21010605 |Yea Ph'aeu (Yea Ph'aeur) |យាផ្អើ |- !6 |21010606 |Ta Mung |តាមូង |} == References == Category:Communes of Takeo Province Category:Angkor Borei District
